Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.76,0:12:54.84,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,（华盛顿）\N{\r原文字幕}♪ Giddy-up, giddy-up ♪ ♪ The snow is falling ♪ ♪ And friends are calling "Yoo Hoo" ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.60,0:12:59.36,原文字幕,,0,0,0,,♪ Friends are calling "Yoo Hoo" ♪ ♪ Ding-a-ling-a-ling ♪
