Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.00,0:27:54.17,原文字幕,,0,0,0,,♪ Sometimes I wonder ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.34,0:27:57.71,原文字幕,,0,0,0,,♪ Why I spend ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.76,0:28:02.30,原文字幕,,0,0,0,,♪ The lonely nights ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.89,0:28:05.85,原文字幕,,0,0,0,,♪ Dreaming of a song ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.51,0:28:08.51,原文字幕,,0,0,0,,♪ The melody ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.97,0:28:11.52,原文字幕,,0,0,0,,♪ Haunts my reverie ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.94,0:28:16.65,原文字幕,,0,0,0,,♪ And I am once again with you ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.19,0:28:21.32,原文字幕,,0,0,0,,♪ When our love was new ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.53,0:28:26.82,原文字幕,,0,0,0,,♪ And each kiss an inspiration ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.87,0:28:34.08,原文字幕,,0,0,0,,♪ But that was long ago ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.08,0:28:37.67,原文字幕,,0,0,0,,♪Now my consolation ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.30,0:28:42.59,原文字幕,,0,0,0,,♪ Is in the stardust of a song ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.72,0:28:48.26,原文字幕,,0,0,0,,♪ Beside a garden wall ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.52,0:28:53.39,原文字幕,,0,0,0,,♪ When stars are bright ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.02,0:28:56.81,原文字幕,,0,0,0,,♪ You are in my arms ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.23,0:28:59.94,原文字幕,,0,0,0,,♪ The nightingale ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.28,0:29:02.94,原文字幕,,0,0,0,,♪ Tells his fairy tale ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.86,0:29:06.95,原文字幕,,0,0,0,,♪ Of paradise where roses grew ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.82,0:29:11.06,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,我可以喝一半啤酒吗？\N{\r原文字幕}Can I have half your beer?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.24,0:29:12.60,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,喝吧\N{\r原文字幕}Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.62,0:29:20.83,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,-我以前都怎么说？\N-“看着你\N{\r原文字幕}What did I use to say? "Here's looking at you"?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.00,0:29:25.11,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,-敬你的眼神”\N-敬我们\N{\r原文字幕}- "Here's mud in your eye"? - "Here's to us."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.29,0:29:29.13,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,你以前都说“敬我们”\N{\r原文字幕}You used to say: "Here's to us."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.13,0:29:37.34,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,宝贝 我想你想到心痛\N{\r原文字幕}Oh, babe. I miss you so much it hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.82,0:29:59.03,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,你说？我说好了\N{\r原文字幕}You want to tell him? I'll tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.20,0:30:02.82,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,他回来了 他又有新点子\N{\r原文字幕}She's back with another idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.00,0:30:08.87,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,山姆 好高兴碰到你 我听到你上电台 我通告全天下了\N{\r原文字幕}Sam, I'm glad you're here. I heard you on the radio. I told everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.05,0:30:13.92,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,-我们已经知道了 葛莉丝\N-等于昭告全西雅图\N{\r原文字幕}- We already knew. From Grace. - Then all of Seattle knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.09,0:30:19.51,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,当时我在刷牙 听到你的声音 马上打给住在赌城的家母\N{\r原文字幕}I was brushing my teeth and there you were. I called my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.68,0:30:24.60,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,叫她收听广播 那可是我的建筑师\N{\r原文字幕}I said, "Turn on the radio. That's my architect."
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.77,0:30:30.86,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,你知道吗 男人肯流露真情 那很感人\N{\r原文字幕}You know, it's so nice when a man can express his feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.03,0:30:35.15,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,-我就做不到\N-克莱尔 设计有什么问题？\N{\r原文字幕}- I wish I could. - Claire, is there a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.32,0:30:39.44,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,我昨晚失眠 你知道那滋味\N{\r原文字幕}I couldn't sleep last night. You know what that's like.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.62,0:30:44.58,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,因为冰箱放不下盘子\N{\r原文字幕}My platters won't fit in the refrigerator.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.75,0:30:50.29,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,我一向用盘子盛点心待客 我就换了个冰箱\N{\r原文字幕}At parties I use platters, so I want a Sub Zero refrigerator instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.46,0:30:55.33,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,-入墙架子得重订\N-得嵌进壁里\N{\r原文字幕}- We have to redo the cabinets. - We'll be into this wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.51,0:31:00.68,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,-那是主墙\N-已经拖了五 六…\N{\r原文字幕}- A bearing wall. - That's a delay of five, six...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.85,0:31:06.72,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,-十二周\N-我不管 做好才重要\N{\r原文字幕}...12 weeks. - It's important to get it right.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.90,0:31:11.48,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,我和设计师还有约 再见\N{\r原文字幕}Well, la decorateur calls. Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.53,0:31:20.15,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,这是命吧 她离婚了 我们不想重做 你少个老婆\N{\r原文字幕}It's fate. She's divorced, we don't want to do this and you need a wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.33,0:31:24.82,译文字幕,,0,0,0,,-当不好的事交错发生应怎么形容？\N-百慕大三角洲\N{\r原文字幕}- Everything intersects. - The Bermuda Triangle.
