Dialogue: 0,1:08:33.81,1:08:36.73,原文字幕,,0,0,0,,♪ Give me a wink and a smile ♪
Dialogue: 0,1:08:48.79,1:08:53.12,原文字幕,,0,0,0,,♪ We go together ♪ ♪ Like a wink and a smile ♪
