Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.84,1:09:04.01,原文字幕,,0,0,0,,♪ Such a simple song ♪
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.43,1:09:09.06,原文字幕,,0,0,0,,♪ Sing it again ♪ ♪ The notes never end ♪
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.77,1:09:12.77,原文字幕,,0,0,0,,♪ This is where I belong ♪
